{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the Nazi salute, like in Germany, and Austria",
        "additional_details": "We think the resurgence of far-right extremism in the UK and Europe is a sobering reality. 80 years after the horrors of World War II, we think the Nazi salute\u2014a symbol of hate, oppression, and genocide\u2014is being dangerously normalised by reckless individuals who trivialise the sacrifices of millions.\r\n \r\nHistory shows us the devastating consequences of allowing hate to flourish. To honour the memory of those who fought for freedom and to safeguard a society built on equality and respect, we think we must ban the Nazi salute.",
        "background": "Please pass legislation that bans the Nazi salute, and condemns individuals, and punishes repeat offenders with fines or imprisonment.",
